wikipedia_page.main: Javed Akhter Khan  was the chief executive of Barnardo's, the UK's largest children's from 2014-2021, having previously been chief executive of Victim Support.

response: * Javed Khan – Chief Executive of Barnardo's, former Chief Executive of the British charity Victim Support; of Kashmiri origin; member of the Whitehall Social Policy Forum; an adviser to the Goldman Sachs Global Leaders Programme
